master api server IP 10.204.51.64
backup api server IP 10.204.51.65
将之前10.204.51.64 的 apiserver scheduler controller-manager 全部复制到 10.204.51.65 对应目录
vip 10.204.51.70
1.首先安装keeaplived 
yum install -y keepalived
2.修改主/etc/keepalived/keepalived.conf
! Configuration File for keepalived
global_defs { 
        router_id LVS_DEVEL
}
vrrp_script check_apiserver {
    script "/etc/keepalived/check.sh"
    interval 3
    weight 2
}
vrrp_instance VI_1 {
    state MASTER
    interface eth0
    virtual_router_id 30
    priority 100 
    advert_int 1
        
    authentication {
        auth_type PASS
        auth_pass 1111
    }
        track_script {
        check_apiserver
    }
     
    virtual_ipaddress {
        10.204.51.70/24
    }

}
3.修改备/etc/keepalived/keepalived.conf

global_defs { 
        router_id LVS_DEVEL
}  
vrrp_script check_apiserver {
    script "/etc/keepalived/check.sh"
    interval 3
    weight 2
} 
vrrp_instance VI_1 {
    state BACKUP
    interface eth0
    virtual_router_id 30
    priority 99 
    advert_int 1
        
    authentication {
        auth_type PASS
        auth_pass 1111
    }
        track_script {
        check_apiserver
    }
     
    virtual_ipaddress {
        10.204.51.70/24
    }

}
4 脚本配置文件 cat /app/kubernetes/scripts/check.sh
#!/bin/bash
netstat -naltp|grep 0.0.0.0:6443
if [ $? = 0 ];
  then
    exit 0
  else
    exit 1 
fi

检查ip是否绑定成功

修改scheduler controller-manager配置
修改scheduler --master=https://10.204.51.70:6443
修改controller-manager--master=https://10.204.51.70:6443
重启scheduler controller-manager

5:主从切换

注意事项:在完成主从切换后，如果主恢复工作，建议将备的api server 重启一次，及systemctl restart kube-apiserver






